<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>中央美院易英博士为郑忠版画撰文《诗化的丝网版画》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200829/60fcfeae2c3342ac84e88569243a7217.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200829/da1ece21e73b450697e7d7812708a51b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
